# Per-version historical benchmark snapshots (`<version>.json`).
#
# Empty as of the v1.0 baseline reset: the pre-1.0 prerelease series
# (1.0.0-beta.0 → 1.0.0-rc.7) was archived (removed) here and lives in git
# history. The floor in `scripts/metrics-history.config.ts` (`since: '1.0.0'`)
# excludes those prereleases from rediscovery, so the trend series starts clean
# at the 1.0.0 stable release.
#
# The first snapshot (`1.0.0.json`) is minted by the post-release metrics-regen
# workflow once 1.0.0 publishes. `import.meta.glob('@/data/metrics/*.json')`
# (benchmarkHistorySources.ts) reads whatever files land here; this .gitkeep is
# not matched by the glob.
